    "en": {
      "title": "Kandakadu Rehabilitation Center Hot - 250 inmates escape",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A tense situation has arisen between the inmates of the Welikanda Kandakadu Drug Rehabilitation Center and the Army following the mysterious death of an inmate this morning (29).",
        "The Army and the Police have been called in to control the situation, Welikanda Police said.",
        "The detainees managed to keep the body of the suspect in the same place as the police or the army could not get it."
      ],
